  "body": "\n\n<center><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/QkZ5VcW/icon.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\"></center>\n\n <br>\n\n<center><a title=\"https://discord.gg/RjWCgrnBZz\" href=\"https://discord.gg/RjWCgrnBZz\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1066142815043719208?color=7289da&label=Discord&logo=discord&logoColor=7289da&style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"\" width=\"314\" height=\"70\"></a></center>\n \n<br>\n\n<center><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/xYmrwP9/description.png\" alt=\"\" ></center>\n\n<br> \n\n- This mod allows you to prevent a player from being able to open the interface of blocks like an Anvil, Enchanting Table, Brewing Stand or a Smithing Table.\n\n- The list of blocks can be edited in the block-guis.toml config file.\n\n<center><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/dcZcCdK/banner-5.png\" alt=\"\" ></center>\n\n# Artists\n- <a href=\"https://linktr.ee/zenokim\">ZenoKim</a>\n\n# Modders\n-  <a href=\"https://www.fiverr.com/shoqapik12\">Shoqapik12</a>\n\n <br>\n\n<center><a title=\"https://billing.kinetichosting.net/aff.php?aff=509\" href=\"https://billing.kinetichosting.net/aff.php?aff=509\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/qR3jbBp/precisemodpacker.png\" alt=\"\"></a></center>\n ",
